        <p>The minimum amount of Certified Raters reviewing each test before a final rating is issued.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 p-item">
        <div class="h3-style">80%</div>
        <p>Percentage of companies that have hired candidates based on false language skills.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

